{"type":"message","id":"60843673","parentId":"abf2a35f","timestamp":"2026-03-18T15:21:41.207Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"根据 clawhub 的搜索结果，我找到了一些相关的 skill，但没有找到专门针对\"多模态文件出题\"的 skill。以下是搜索结果：\n\n**与出题/测验相关的：**\n- `quiz-generator` - Quiz Generator (3.372) - 可能是最相关的\n- `quiz` - Quiz (3.408)\n- `quiz-battle` - Quiz Battle (3.374)\n- `trivia-quiz` - Trivia Quiz (3.353)\n- `xueersi-daily-question` - 学而思每日一题生成器 (3.029)\n- `interview-question-gen` - 面试题生成器 (2.941)\n\n**与文件处理相关的：**\n- `local-file-rag-basic` - 本地文件 RAG 基础版 (3.407)\n- `pdf-extract` - PDF 提取 (3.604)\n- `nano-pdf` - Nano PDF (3.748)\n- `visual-file-sorter` - 视觉系文件分类大师 (3.369)\n\n**目前看来没有专门的多模态文件出题 skill**。最接近的方案是：\n1. `quiz-generator` + `pdf-extract`/`local-file-rag-basic` 组合使用\n2. 或者需要你自己创建一个这样的 skill\n\n老大需要我帮你看看某个具体 skill 的详情，还是你有兴趣自己造一个？🐉"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":183,"output":292,"cacheRead":17408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17883,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773847295502}}
