{"type":"message","id":"89e17ddc","parentId":"1b46654b","timestamp":"2026-03-18T15:37:17.705Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完成了老大！🎉 给你总结一下这个 skill：\n\n## 📦 multimodal-quiz-generator 已创建\n\n**位置：** `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multimodal-quiz-generator/`\n\n**打包文件：** `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/multimodal-quiz-generator.skill`\n\n---\n\n### 功能结构\n\n| 组件 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `extract_pdf.py` | PDF 文本提取 |\n| `extract_docx.py` | Word 文档提取 |\n| `extract_pptx.py` | PPT 内容提取 |\n| `extract_excel.py` | Excel 内容提取 |\n| `transcribe_media.py` | 音视频转录（支持 Whisper）|\n| `generate_quiz.py` | 题目生成主脚本 |\n\n---\n\n### 使用方法\n\n```bash\n# 1. 提取文件内容\npython scripts/extract_pdf.py document.pdf > content.txt\n\n# 2. 生成题目（直接打印）\npython scripts/generate_quiz.py --input content.txt --count 6\n```\n\n---\n\n### 目前状态\n\n- ✅ SKILL.md 完成\n- ✅ 6 个提取脚本完成\n- ✅ 题目模板文档完成\n- ✅ AI Prompt 模板完成\n- ⚠️ `generate_quiz.py` 目前是模板实现，需要接入 LLM API 才能真正生成题目\n\n---\n\n### 下一步（如果需要）\n\n1. **接入 LLM**：把 `generate_quiz.py` 改成调用 OpenAI/Claude/Kimi API 真正生成题目\n2. **安装依赖**：`pip install PyPDF2 pdfplumber python-docx python-pptx openpyxl openai`\n3. **发布到 clawhub**：`clawhub publish ./multimodal-quiz-generator`\n\n需要我帮你接入 LLM 实现真正的题目生成吗？🐉"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":287,"output":404,"cacheRead":33280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33971,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773848229567}}
